{"tid":2073002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度跨黨派撐「回應中國侵略」 莫迪為衝突降溫 稱解放軍無越界","createTime":"2020-06-21T04:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T04:43:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"29ff3373ed16622fcf2a31bbd26900e54d08b223","tid":2073002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200621/2K6SBGDV6H7GPCXOXCF5USQP6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200621%2F2K6SBGDV6H7GPCXOXCF5USQP6M%2F&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=cc217d8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200621%2F2K6SBGDV6H7GPCXOXCF5USQP6M%2F&h=703393c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200621/2K6SBGDV6H7GPCXOXCF5USQP6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n印度跨黨派撐「回應中國侵略」<br />\n莫迪為衝突降溫 稱解放軍無越界<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中印邊境緊張局勢升溫，印度總理莫迪前日邀請各黨領袖召開所有政黨會議，多個政黨領袖都表示支持印度政府「對中國侵略作出回應」。但莫迪其後嘗試為事件降溫，指出「沒有外國勢力軍隊越過邊境入侵印度」。另外，有印媒報道指，日前兩軍毆鬥中，解放軍正副指揮官俱陣亡，又指印方近日已向邊境增兵1.5萬。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪當日邀請了各個黨派的領袖參與視像會議，在會上保證印度軍方會盡一切能力保衞國家，在今次事件中也展示出沒有人可以奪走印度領土。他同時強調印度渴望和平與友誼，也有意於中國保持友好，但捍衞主權凌駕一切。與會的在野黨及反對黨均對莫迪表示支持，稱「團結以成為軍隊的後盾」，以回應中方的侵略，並讓解放軍退回到中印邊境實際控制線的位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/347326BPTDGRYCWNQIBJV6RMUU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F347326BPTDGRYCWNQIBJV6RMUU.gif&h=69f29cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫迪在跨黨會議上強調捍衞主權凌駕一切。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4TCBVX5G365XQCLVACE4Y7WP7E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4TCBVX5G365XQCLVACE4Y7WP7E.gif&h=a001268f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊境衝突後，印度爆發反華浪潮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55UCKTLMZ2GGXV26KNWVVH5IRM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55UCKTLMZ2GGXV26KNWVVH5IRM.gif&h=b55466e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度人砸壞中國製產品洩憤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不符外長說法 料欲保持友好<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：防節外生枝 華官媒冷待<br />\n<br />\n極右政黨濕婆。。。。。，堅決支持莫迪的決定。」<br />\n<br />\n然而，莫迪在會後發表電視聲明時卻表現得較溫和，雖稱「誓言在必要時將使用軍事力量保衞領土邊界」，卻也指出。。。。。關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印媒：解放軍正副指揮官陣亡<br />\n<br />\n同日晚，中國外交部發言人趙立堅。。。。。，造成人員傷亡」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《印度斯坦時報》又引述另一名印度高級官員指，中國試圖改變兩國邊境的現狀，。。。。。。目前雙方仍自說自話，沒有一個統一版本出台。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，截至6月18日，中印邊境東中西全線，印度軍隊幾乎處於戰爭戒備狀態，更在前線部署超過1.5萬名士兵。<br />\n<br />\n《印度斯坦時報》/美聯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社"},{"pid":"96c002b2e774f73e538dd49b5386b3054a5334d5","tid":2073002,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:28:00.000Z","msg":"印度咁快跪"},{"pid":"caa11aaabfe2f1e6808620368a52ce6aa730ed95","tid":2073002,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"去撥火，支那無越界咁邊個越界<br />\n屌尻咖哩越界，話佢地抵死<br />\n仲屌尻佢地非法殺害解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc549d683617989c4fdec4b75fb030f6c2386256","tid":2073002,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3100fe95982d412c0f4bef23c37bd5618470f49b","tid":2073002,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"過左數算啦唔打啦"},{"pid":"9fba77b6de9060ecd039ad7ff6caa9fbff927a6c","tid":2073002,"uid":35470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"好難跪，佢本身係靠民族主義，加埋聽電台話佢係低種姓人士，一跪就好麻煩"},{"pid":"1b79cd084689c9e52652e485f398dd71ea9a018a","tid":2073002,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:39:25.000Z","msg":"屌你莫迪無撚用"},{"pid":"de13ec43b2f94f65d92efe23c5056cbe3e94ef7c","tid":2073002,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:39:52.000Z","msg":"個黨好型 叫濕婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33922305cfcf3817e8c990997b51775f21e5e35b","tid":2073002,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"班阿叉都係無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返去食蕉啦"},{"pid":"024c3ab51bed2e64dfe716c131786e389becf958","tid":2073002,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"樓上做乜鳩<br />\n而家係得個總理想跪"},{"pid":"66fa3730cd8ca3c8f9b184c8597c103fae668202","tid":2073002,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:43:07.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"}]}